nl.naturalis.lims2.ab1.importer

Class LimsImportAB1

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.plugin.DocumentFileImporter
      • nl.naturalis.lims2.ab1.importer.LimsImportAB1

  • public class LimsImportAB1
extends com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.plugin.DocumentFileImporter
    Date: 24 august 2016
    Company: Naturalis Biodiversity Center
    City: Leiden
    Country: Netherlands
    Description:
    Start Geneious.
    Click on the "Import" button.
    Go to the AB1/Fasta files you want to import.
    Choose "All Naturalis files" from the dropdown menu of "Files of Type" in the dialog screen and press "Import".
    Import process is started.
    A dialog window appears with a progress bar with a message.
    Author:
    Reinier.Kartowikromo
